    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/03.mp3'
    
    "----Hmm."
    
    "I probably won't ever get a chance to talk with Arcueid in a fast food restaurant in the middle of the day like this again, so I'll ask not about vampires, but something more ordinary."
    
    "\"Then I'll ask you."
    
    "Arcueid, could you tell me a little about your interests, your past, and your three sizes?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"You want to know about that?"
    
    "You sure ask strange things, Shiki.\""
    
    "\"It's not strange."
    
    "I don't know anything about you, so it's natural to want to know about you.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Ah, I feel the same way, perhaps----in that case, I don't mind.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"But, interests and a past.. I don't have any of those."
    
    "I've also never measured myself so I can't tell you my three sizes."
    
    "I never recorded my age or my height like you guys do.\""
    
    "\"What do you mean?"
    
    "You've never even wondered about yourself?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01B.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"No, it's not like that, but it wasn't anything I ever had as a priority."
    
    "All I need is the ability to hunt Dead Apostles.... vampires.\""
    
    "\"But still, there were things that happened before you came to this city, right?"
    
    "I want to hear about those kinds of things.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Before I came here.... hmm, that would probably be about eight years ago then."
    
    "At that time, I wasn't in this country, but in some other country hunting a vampire."
    
    "A vampire made its lair in a small, French countryside village that became a ghost town."
    
    "After two days, I found the 'enemy' and dealt with the female Dead Apostle controlling the town----\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "As if remembering something horrible, Arcueid closes her eyes and cuts off."
    
    "\"Eight years ago?"
    
    "Then up until now, what were you doing, Arcueid?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01B.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"What was I doing?"
    
    "I just went back to my castle and slept."
    
    "My duty is to hunt Dead Apostles."
    
    "I have no other meaning for existence, so until another Dead Apostle stands out, there's nothing to do but continue sleeping, right?\""
    
    "\"Wha------\""
    
    "Continue sleeping?"
    
    "Does she mean literally?"
    
    "No, in the first place----"
    
    "\".... Wait a minute."
    
    "A castle, you mean that castle?"
    
    "I'd have trouble believing it, but don't tell me your place is like that Cinderella's castle..!?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T11.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Cinderella's castle?\""
    
    "Arcueid tilts her head like she doesn't get it."
    
    "\"Uh----no, that's not a really appropriate expression."
    
    "Um, I mean, you're a, um.... princess?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Yes, it seems that way."
    
    "A long time ago I was told not to cut my hair and scolded to act more like royalty.\""
    
    "\"--------\""
    
    ".... I'm speechless."
    
    "Come to think of it, that Nrvnqsr guy always called her \"princess.\""
    
    "But still----"
    
    "\"A royal princess?\""
    
    "I steal a glance at Arcueid."
    
    "She's beautiful enough to take your breath away, but such a rambunctious person a princess?"
    
    "She's not quite what comes to mind when I think of a princess."
    
    "\".... Well, at least you are as selfish as a princess.\""
    
    "I give a deep sigh."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T16.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Hey now!"
    
    "I only said it because you asked, so don't respond like that!\""
    
    "Her Royal Highness glares at me."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    ".... Arcueid doesn't seem to think of herself as a princess either, so I think it's just best to forget about this."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_56.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Still angry, Arcueid resumes eating her hamburger."
    
    "After she's finished and calmed down, we decide to go somewhere else."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
